hwSmartLinkMib.contactinfo: Huawei Industrial Base Bantian, Longgang Shenzhen 518129 People's Republic of China Website: http://www.huawei.com Email: support@huawei.com
hwSmartLinkMib.description: This module includes the information about smart link. The information can be read and some of them can be set.

hwSmartLinkRevFlushTotal.name: hwSmartLinkRevFlushTotal
hwSmartLinkRevFlushTotal.description: The total of received flush packets.

hwSmartLinkRevLastFlushIfIndex.name: hwSmartLinkRevLastFlushIfIndex
hwSmartLinkRevLastFlushIfIndex.description: The interface index of port which received flush packet lastly.

hwSmartLinkRevLastFlushTime.name: hwSmartLinkRevLastFlushTime
hwSmartLinkRevLastFlushTime.description: The time when received flush packet lastly. field octets contents range - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 1 1-2 year 0..65536 2 3 month 1..12 3 4 day 1..31 4 5 hour 0..23 5 6 minutes 0..59 6 7 seconds 0..60 (use 60 for leap-second) 7 8 deci-seconds 0..9

hwSmartLinkRevLastFlushSourceMacAddr.name: hwSmartLinkRevLastFlushSourceMacAddr
hwSmartLinkRevLastFlushSourceMacAddr.description: The SMAC of flush packet which arrived this device lastly.

hwSmartLinkRevLastFlushVlan.name: hwSmartLinkRevLastFlushVlan
hwSmartLinkRevLastFlushVlan.description: The control VLAN of flush packet which arrived this device lastly.

hwSmartLinkResetFlushStatistics.name: hwSmartLinkResetFlushStatistics
hwSmartLinkResetFlushStatistics.description: Reset the statistics of flush packets.

hwSmartLinkRevPortCfgTable.name: hwSmartLinkRevPortCfgTable
hwSmartLinkRevPortCfgTable.description: This is port configuration table which received flush packet, and configuration relation of port received flush packet was described. The index of table is hwSmartLinkRpcIfIndex.

hwSmartLinkRevPortCfgEntry.name: hwSmartLinkRevPortCfgEntry
hwSmartLinkRevPortCfgEntry.description: The table includes the information of the received flush packet port configuration information. The index of the table is hwSmartLinkRpcIfIndex.

hwSmartLinkRpcIfIndex.name: hwSmartLinkRpcIfIndex
hwSmartLinkRpcIfIndex.description: The index of port from which received flush packets.

hwSmartLinkRpcRevVlan.name: hwSmartLinkRpcRevVlan
hwSmartLinkRpcRevVlan.description: Set the VLAN ID to verify the validity of flush packets received. Ranging from 1 to 4094.

hwSmartLinkRpcRevPassword.name: hwSmartLinkRpcRevPassword
hwSmartLinkRpcRevPassword.description: Set the password to verify the validity of flush packets received.

hwSmartLinkRpcRevAuthMode.name: hwSmartLinkRpcRevAuthMode
hwSmartLinkRpcRevAuthMode.description: Set the password mode to verify the validity of flush packets received.

hwSmartLinkGroupCfgTable.name: hwSmartLinkGroupCfgTable
hwSmartLinkGroupCfgTable.description: The table includes the information of the smart link group configuration information, and include the mode of smart link group, working status of group, control vlan of group etc.

hwSmartLinkGroupCfgEntry.name: hwSmartLinkGroupCfgEntry
hwSmartLinkGroupCfgEntry.description: The table includes the information of the smart link group configuration information. The index of the table is hwSmartLinkGcGroupId.

hwSmartLinkGcMasterIfIndex.name: hwSmartLinkGcMasterIfIndex
hwSmartLinkGcMasterIfIndex.description: The master interface index of smart link group.

hwSmartLinkGcSlaveIfIndex.name: hwSmartLinkGcSlaveIfIndex
hwSmartLinkGcSlaveIfIndex.description: The slave interface index of smart link group.

hwSmartLinkGcGroupStatus.name: hwSmartLinkGcGroupStatus
hwSmartLinkGcGroupStatus.description: Working status of smart link group, include none, master, slave, idle and init. none: all ports in group are inactive. Master: master port is active, and slave port is inactive. Slave: master port is inactive, and slave port is active. Idle: smart-link group is disable, and all ports are inactive. Init: smart-link group is enable, and all ports are inactive.

hwSmartLinkGcEnable.name: hwSmartLinkGcEnable
hwSmartLinkGcEnable.description: Startup or close the smart link group. Before startup the smart link group, the group must be created.

hwSmartLinkGcSendControlVlan.name: hwSmartLinkGcSendControlVlan
hwSmartLinkGcSendControlVlan.description: Set the tag of flush packets which send from this smart link group.

hwSmartLinkGcSendPassword.name: hwSmartLinkGcSendPassword
hwSmartLinkGcSendPassword.description: Set password of flush packets which send from this smart link group.

hwSmartLinkGcLock.name: hwSmartLinkGcLock
hwSmartLinkGcLock.description: Active port was locked on master port

hwSmartLinkGcForce.name: hwSmartLinkGcForce
hwSmartLinkGcForce.description: Active port was locked on slave port.

hwSmartLinkGcRevertEnable.name: hwSmartLinkGcRevertEnable
hwSmartLinkGcRevertEnable.description: When wait-to-restore timer is over, the smart link group link will be switched.

hwSmartLinkGcManual.name: hwSmartLinkGcManual
hwSmartLinkGcManual.description: The link was switched every setting manual command.

hwSmartLinkGcRowStatus.name: hwSmartLinkGcRowStatus
hwSmartLinkGcRowStatus.description: Status of smart link group row.

hwSmartLinkGcAuthMode.name: hwSmartLinkGcAuthMode
hwSmartLinkGcAuthMode.description: Set the password mode of flush packets which send from this smart link group.

hwSmartLinkPortCfgTable.name: hwSmartLinkPortCfgTable
hwSmartLinkPortCfgTable.description: This table is the configuration table of member port of smart link group. This table described that configuration relation of member port of smart link group. This table index is hwSmartLinkPcGroupId and hwSmartLinkPcPortType.

hwSmartLinkPortCfgEntry.name: hwSmartLinkPortCfgEntry
hwSmartLinkPortCfgEntry.description: This table described that configuration relation of member port of smart link group. This table index is hwSmartLinkPcGroupId and hwSmartLinkPcPortType.

hwSmartLinkPcPortType.name: hwSmartLinkPcPortType
hwSmartLinkPcPortType.description: The role of smart link group member port.

hwSmartLinkPcIfIndex.name: hwSmartLinkPcIfIndex
hwSmartLinkPcIfIndex.description: Interface index of member port of smart link group.

hwSmartLinkPcPortStatus.name: hwSmartLinkPcPortStatus
hwSmartLinkPcPortStatus.description: The status of member port, include unknown, active and inactive.

hwSmartLinkPcSendFlushNum.name: hwSmartLinkPcSendFlushNum
hwSmartLinkPcSendFlushNum.description: The total of flush packets send from this port.

hwSmartLinkPcSendFlushTime.name: hwSmartLinkPcSendFlushTime
hwSmartLinkPcSendFlushTime.description: The time when send flush packet lastly. field octets contents range - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 1 1-2 year 0..65536 2 3 month 1..12 3 4 day 1..31 4 5 hour 0..23 5 6 minutes 0..59 6 7 seconds 0..60 (use 60 for leap-second) 7 8 deci-seconds 0..9

hwSmartLinkPcRowStatus.name: hwSmartLinkPcRowStatus
hwSmartLinkPcRowStatus.description: Status of monitor link group row.

hwMonitorLinkGroupCfgTable.name: hwMonitorLinkGroupCfgTable

hwMonitorLinkGroupCfgEntry.name: hwMonitorLinkGroupCfgEntry
hwMonitorLinkGroupCfgEntry.description: This is status information table of monitor link group, and index is hwMonitorLinkGcGroupId.

hwMonitorLinkGcRecoverTime.name: hwMonitorLinkGcRecoverTime

hwMonitorLinkGcRowStatus.name: hwMonitorLinkGcRowStatus
hwMonitorLinkGcRowStatus.description: Status of monitor link group row.

hwMonitorLinkUlPortType.description: Type of uplink port in monitor link group, include smart link group and switch port.

hwMonitorLinkUlPortValue.description: When port type is smart link, the value is smart link group index. When port type is switch port, the value is ifindex of switch port.
